      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "1. 清除 localStorage\n   ├─ access token\n   ├─ refresh token\n   └─ user info\n\n2. 重置 userStore 状态\n\n3. 跳转到登录页面\n   router.push('/login')",
      "textAlign": "left",
